<h2 id="story-16-authenticated-users-security">Story 16: Authenticated users security</h2>

<p>Background: An authenticated user</p>

<p>As an Authenticated User
I cannot view another userâ€™s private data (current or past orders, etc)
I cannot view the administrator screens or use admin functionality
I cannot make myself an admin</p>

<h2 id="story-17-unauthenticated-users-security">Story 17: Unauthenticated users security</h2>

<p>Background: An unauthenticated user and their abilities</p>

<p>As an Unauthenticated User
I cannot view another userâ€™s private data, such as current order, etc.
I should be redirected to login/create account when I try to check out.
I cannot view the administrator screens or use administrator functionality.
I cannot make myself an administrator.</p>

