<h2 id="story-29-retired-item-analytics">Story 29: Retired Item Analytics</h2>

<p>On the analytics-dashboard
I see a list of items that have ever been retired, including their item name, current status (retired or active) and total retired count. Items should be ordered by how many times they have been retired (retired count).</p>

